This paper discusses the privacy vulnerabilities in LTE networks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the implementation of appropriate mechanisms to mitigate attacks, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper presents experimental results, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
